# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

## Dependencies & Lockfiles
# Ignore node_modules directories in ANY folder (the main fix)
**/node_modules/

# Ignore dependency cache and pnp files
.pnp
.pnp.js

## Build & Production Artifacts
# Ignore build output folders
**/build/
**/dist/
.out/
**/.next/

## Testing & Coverage Reports
# Ignore testing and coverage output
**/coverage/
**/coverage-report/
.nyc_output

## Environment Variables
# Ignore all local environment files.
# Commit .env.example to show what variables are needed.
.env.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local
.env.*.local

## Logs
# Ignore log files from npm, yarn, and other tools
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
*.log

## IDE & Editor Directories
# Ignore metadata folders from popular IDEs and editors
.idea/
.vscode/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

## Operating System Files
# Ignore files generated by macOS, Windows, and Linux systems
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
._*
*~

## Miscellaneous
# Ignore temporary files or other generated content
/**.cmd
